OH Max = (OH Weapon Max + Bonus Max)
MH Avg = (MH Min + MH Max) / 2 + MH Bonus Damage
OH Avg = (OH Min + OH Max) / 2 + OH Bonus Damage
A = (MH Avg + OH Avg) / 2</pre>
